    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half</p><p>Trim the green stalks off the <strong>aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and cut lengthways then dice into bite-sized pieces</p>",
