      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced aubergine</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min until starting to brown</p>",
