    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the aubergine is browning, chop the <strong>cucumber</strong> into quarters, lengthways, then chop roughly</p><p>Chop the <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Roughly chop the <strong>black olives</strong></p>",
