      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is browned, reduce the heat to medium and add the <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>garlic paste</strong> and juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the aubergine is cooked through and softened – this is your <strong>Greek-style aubergine</strong></p>",
